<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

<h2>Is Chumpol Trading Group a humanitarian organization?</h2>
<p><strong>No.</strong> Chumpol Trading Group is a B2B trading company.</p>

<h2>Is Chumpol Trading Group a financial services company?</h2>
<p><strong>No.</strong></p>

<h2>Does Chumpol Trading Group operate an online shop?</h2>
<p><strong>No.</strong></p>

<h2>Does Chumpol Trading Group sell to private customers?</h2>
<p><strong>No.</strong> Only business-to-business (B2B).</p>

<h2>Is Chumpol Trading Group connected to other CTG companies?</h2>
<p><strong>No.</strong> There is no affiliation with other organizations using the abbreviation CTG.</p>

<h2>What does Chumpol Trading Group do?</h2>
<p>
Chumpol Trading Group is a Thailand-based B2B distributor for consumer electronics and wholesale trading.
</p>

